formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	It is the responsibility of management to prepare the financial statement of firm. The firm has prepared financial statement by following the mercantile method of accounting. The promoter has passed all necessary entries in accounts and reported all bank accounts in the financial statements and based on the unaudited accounts produced before us for given this certificate and relied on same for reporting to RERA Authority while certifying Form 3.
2.	The compilation & certification of figures in the said RERA Form - 3 along-with applicable annexure are based & relied on  management and other professional
3.	Amount deposited and withdrawn from the bank account reflects only booking receipts collected and utilized in the project.
4.	Management of the entity has provided Customer ID, details of PAN / Aadhar Card, and Mobile Numbers of the allottees, Date of Registered Agreement for sale and Encumbrance Status and we have relied on the same while giving this certificate.
5.	As per Information and explanation received from the promoter has directly executed Sale deed to the allotees without entering registered agreement for sale hence, in Column or detail of Date of Agreement for sale, we have entered sale deed for reporting purpose. 
6.	The Promoter has repaid secured loan taken from STATE Bank of India and hence In Encumbrance Status, However, because no NOC produced before us by the management, we have given created in Encumbrance Status.
